  <p>Glyphic Phantomreaper writes:</p>
  <blockquote><font color=beige>
<p>In the lake rathe arena there was a Race wars event. It was humans vs darks vs shorts vs elfs. Human team had 11 players. Shorts = 14. Darks = 12 and elfs =6. Shorties won with 11 players still alive. Elves and humans were finished off first. Darks last. Every player on short team won 256pp. Which was a split of all the money entered to participate in the event. (3pp times you lvl, lvls 40 and lower only). Gratz to the pecks who fought surprisingly well. Hope to see and join in more events on Vallon in the future.</p>
Glyphic Phantomreaper<br> World Theory<br> AntiPaladin of the 39th shadow<br>
