  <blockquote><font color=beige>
    <p>I was in Qeynos Hills and saw a message stating that something was 
    stirring in BB, more gnoll activity than usual.<br>
    <br>
    I headed into BB to check it out. I noticed there is a new gnoll, a gnoll 
    tactician. When I killed it, he dropped "battle plans." Though they are in a 
    gnoll language I cannot read.<br>
    <br>
    Also I found a named NPC, a human Scout, hiding under the bridge near the 
    pitfall trap. He did not respond to my hails.<br>
    <br>
    The gnolls are also dropping much more weapons and armor than they used 
    to... I think they are planning to invade Surefall Glade or perhaps Qeynos.</p>
  </blockquote></font>
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
